<div type="content">
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l3"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . bey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>heydenab<ex>er</ex></expan> nehſt ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l4"><expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> teten . daʒ vns
                        Reinhart von hohenart <expan>gena<ex>n</ex>t</expan> frey
                                <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> diener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l5"><expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef geſandt vnd
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſacʒ aufgeſagt hett als dıe
                                <expan>yngeſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l6">ſeins brıefs auſʒweıſt .
                            <expan>Demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> wır auch <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l7"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ʒuſage<ex>n</ex></expan> . daʒ vns niht wıſſend
                            <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> daʒ <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
                        Reinhart </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l8">ye kein ſacʒ beredt <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . ſo
                                <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> wır auch
