                                <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l10">vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> / daʒ ſıe
                        keinrley <expan>weſte<ex>n</ex></expan> mit
                            <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan> ʒuſchıken ʒu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l11">eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> darauf
                                <expan>ʒubıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vns eẅr gnade vnd guten
                                <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> ın den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ʒu be - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l12"><expan>weıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / da mıt der
                                <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan> . <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> ſölıch fehe gen vns abteͣt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l13"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wır wol / daʒ ſıch
                        eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade
                                    <expan><expan>darinn<ex>en</ex></expan></expan> gemẅet vnd mıt
