</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l14"><expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> geredt hat / Des wır
                            <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ
                            <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan> . Alſo hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l15"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Cancʒl<ex>er</ex></expan> auf dıſʒ ʒeıt ein
                            <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> ʒubracht / der auf ſölıch
                                <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> auſʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l16">weıſt / daʒ der
                            <expan>eg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>beken<ex>n</ex>t</expan> . Vmb den ſacʒ der vor
                                <expan>ʒeıte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l17">ſein beteıdıngt ſey <expan>word<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        von ſprüch <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe er ʒu vns hab . den ſacʒ wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l18"><expan>beıd<ex>er</ex>ſeıt</expan> ein
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>aufſage<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> mondt vor . Alſo well er vmb
                                <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l19">dıe ſache in gut beſteen
                            <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / Alſo wurd er mıt vns niht gerıcht vmb
