<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l20">ſprüch . ſo möcht er vns den ſacʒ
                                <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>aufſage<ex>n</ex></expan> vıer <expan>woche<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt
                                <expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l21"><expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> etc Vnd warb der
                                <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Cancʒl<ex>er</ex></expan> darauf . Jm <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
                        von dem <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l22"><expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> . geͣben wır Jm
                            <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſölıchen <expan>offen<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> . <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>Jnſ<ex>igel</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l23">ſo ſölt er vns <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan>
<expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> auch <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> /
                                <expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> nu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır keinrley </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l24">ſprüche dıe er ʒu vns hab . ſo
                            <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır vns auch ſeıd nehſt von des ſacʒ
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l25">bas erfarn vnd <expan>könne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>nyend<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>finde<ex>n</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> .
                                <expan>ſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd
                            <expan>Regıſt<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / Daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l26"><expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>deſſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Reinh<ex>art</ex></expan> ye kein ſacʒ beteıdıngt ſey . Daʒ wır denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l27">ſöllıch <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> von Jm
                            <expan>neͣme</expan> vnd <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> . damit wır Jm vrſache </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l28">geͣben als ob er ſprüch ʒu vns hett /
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> vns <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> ſacʒ
                                <expan>aufſage<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht wenn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_460_r2l29">er wölt / mag eẅr
                            <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / daʒvns das ſwer vnd vnfüklıch
